The '''Half Transmogrified Junction''' is as it's name suggests, half of a [[en/Community/Junctionary/Transmogrified]] Junction.

[[File:en/Community/Junctionary/Ttd.half.transmogrified.variant.png|frame|none|Halve getransformeerde kruising met bruggen]]

===Voordelen===
*Quite fast.
*Quite compact.
*Traffic jams are unlikely since tracks split before they merge.
*No loops.

===Nadelen===
*The slopes makes some trains go slower. 

